ActOther Than Statutory Authority
SubjectAddition to Lac Simon Indian Reserve, Quebec
PrecisOrder setting apart 354.655 hectares (876.372 acres) of land for the use and benefit of the Anishnable Lac Simon First Nation as an addition to LAC SIMON INDIAN RESERVE, located in the Louvicourt and Vauquelin Townships at approximately 32 kilometres from Val d'Or, Quebec.
